==事故==
[[File:UP_Macdona_Derailment.jpg|left]]
2004年6月28日，一列UP列車和BNSF列車在德克薩斯州麥克唐納相撞，造成約90噸[[氯氣|液氯]]泄漏，形成致命性“黃霧”。共有三人死亡 (一人為UP車長，另兩人為附近居民)，43人入院治療。事故造成財產損失於善後處理共耗資7百萬美元。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.aristatek.com/newsletter/0708August/TechSpeak.pdf |title= Chlorine Rail Car Incident |publisher= Aristatek |accessdate= April 18, 2010 |archive-date= 2013-10-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131015232621/http://www.aristatek.com/newsletter/0708August/TechSpeak.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>

近年的另一起脫軌事故發生於1994年德克薩斯州聖安東尼奧附近的[[比尔县_(得克萨斯州)|比爾縣]]，並造成一人死亡。參議院Kay·Hutchinson向聯邦政府申請對此次事故調查。<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/11/national/11derail.html |title= Man Killed in Fifth Train Derailment in San Antonio Since May |work= New York Times |accessdate= April 18, 2010 |date= November 11, 2004 |archive-date= 2015-01-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150107231604/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/11/national/11derail.html |dead-url= no }}</ref> 

曾有許多居住在鐵路附近的人士要求聯合太平洋將運送危險化學品的列車改道，不再經由市區或居民區。 2005年3月，德州州長[[里克·佩里|里克·佩里]]宣布將支持UP的改線計劃，危險品列車將不再從從城鎮和高密度人口區穿行。<ref name="query.nytimes.com">{{cite news | url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DE7DA113CF93AA25750C0A9639C8B63 | work=The New York Times | first=Walt | last=Bogdanich | title=Texas Has Pact With Railroad To Move Lines | date=March 19, 2005 | accessdate=2012-11-18 | archive-date=2012-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111113236/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DE7DA113CF93AA25750C0A9639C8B63 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

麥克唐納鎮事故調查揭示了聯合太平洋鐵路部分安全隱患。“聯邦鐵道管理局 (FRA)”於同年發表的官方調查結果表明，UP在此次事故中存在部分員工忽視公司安全守則，列車車組疲勞駕駛等。<ref name="nytimes.com">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/17/politics/17rail.html | work=The New York Times | first1=Jenny | last1=Nordberg | first2=Walt | last2=Bogdanich | title=Regulators Plan to Step Up Union Pacific Safety Checks | date=November 17, 2004 | accessdate=2012-11-18 | archive-date=2013-05-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517191431/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/17/politics/17rail.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 此外，聯合太平洋鐵路在組織上亦對事故有著“不可推卸的責任”，裝載液氯的罐車被不合理的至於編組前部。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ntsb.gov/speeches/sumwalt/rls070522.htm |title= NTSB – Remarks by Robert L. Sumwalt |publisher= National Transportation Safety Board |accessdate= April 19, 2010 |archive-date= 2010-12-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101220103727/http://ntsb.gov/Speeches/sumwalt/rls070522.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref> 根據慣例，裝載危險品的車輛應當位於編組後部，一方面減少發生一般撞車事故時波及的概率，另一方面也避免貨車和機車相撞造成嚴重的二次損害。

作為麥克唐納鎮事故事故的後續，2004年11月，聯邦鐵道管理局和UP簽署一項備忘錄，要求每一項被FRA監督員發現的安全隱患都應當被“立即改正”。<ref name="query.nytimes.com"/><ref name="nytimes.com"/>此外，FRA要求公司加強對員工的安全教育，並且增加FRA安全監督員的數量。<ref name="nytimes.com"/>然而聯邦眾議員Charlie Gonzalez質疑這份備忘錄是否真的能起有效監管作用。他和其他一些國會議員在紐約時報發表文章稱FRA的首長Betty Monro和UP的首席掮客Mary E. McAuliffe私交過密，“多次一起在南塔基特島渡假”。<ref name="nytimes.com"/>

隨後的數年內，UP聖安東尼奧中心所屬路段多次發生脫軌事故。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pro8news.com/news/local/86466522.html |title= Train derailment leaves big mess |publisher= pro8news |accessdate= April 18, 2010 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100308133352/http://www.pro8news.com/news/local/86466522.html |archivedate= 2010年3月8日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.mysanantonio.com/news/Train_derails_near_New_Braunfels_without_injuries.html |title= Train derails near New Braunfels |publisher= San Antonio Express News |accessdate= April 18, 2010 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.mysanantonio.com/news/local_news/Union_Pacific_train_derails_in_Atascosa_County.html |title= UP train derails in Atascosa County |publisher= San Antonio Express News |accessdate= April 18, 2010 |archive-date= 2012-09-04 |archive-url= https://archive.is/20120904012918/http://www.mysanantonio.com/news/local_news/article/UP-train-derails-in-Atascosa-County-840581.php |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.victoriaadvocate.com/news/2009/jun/15/er_train_derailment_061609_54757/ |title= Train derails near Schulenburg, spills chemical |publisher= The Victoria Advocate |accessdate= April 15, 2010 |archive-date= 2011-10-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20111003124615/http://www.victoriaadvocate.com/news/2009/jun/15/er_train_derailment_061609_54757/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>2009年，一列滿載液氯和[[石腦油|石腦油]]的列車在德克薩斯州舒倫堡脫軌，所幸並未發生泄漏。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.epaosc.org/site/site_profile.aspx?site_id=5112 |title= Schulenburg Train Derailment |publisher= United States Environmental Protection Agency |accessdate=April 18, 2010}}</ref>

2012年6月24日，兩輛UP列車在[[俄克拉何馬城|俄克拉何馬城]]西北300英里處的古德維爾相撞，機車燃油泄漏造成大火，造成三名車組人員死亡。當時，一輛列車應當停在測線待避另一輛通過。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2012/jun/26/ntsb-why-didnt-train-wait-oklahoma-crash/?page=all |title= NTSB: Why didn’t train wait before Oklahoma crash? |publisher= The Washington Times |date= June 26, 2012 |accessdate= July 19, 2012 |archive-date= 2015-12-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151222094703/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2012/jun/26/ntsb-why-didnt-train-wait-oklahoma-crash/?page=all |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2012年11月15日，在德克薩斯州[[米德蘭_(德克薩斯州)|米德蘭]]，UP列車在道口和一輛遊行花車相撞，造成參加老兵紀念活動的4名退伍老兵死亡。

